# рџЏ‹пёЏ TrivionX вЂ“ AI Gym & Fitness Assistant

## рџ“Њ Overview

**TrivionX** is an AI-powered fitness assistant developed using **Python** and **Streamlit**. It provides users with personalized health insights, workout planning, diet recommendations, PDF-based knowledge retrieval, and fitness tracking through an interactive dashboard.

The objective of this project is to provide a one-stop fitness companion that helps users achieve their health goals using Artificial Intelligence and data-driven recommendations.

---

# вњЁ Features

## рџ“Џ BMI Calculator

* Calculates Body Mass Index (BMI)
* Displays BMI category
* Provides daily calorie estimation

---

## рџҐ— AI Dietician

* Personalized Indian diet plans
* Supports:

  * Weight Loss
  * Muscle Gain
  * Weight Maintenance
* Vegetarian and Non-Vegetarian options
* Calculates recommended daily calories
* Collects:

  * Age
  * Height
  * Weight
  * Gender
  * Fitness Goal

---

## рџ’Є AI Workout Planner

* Generates weekly workout schedules
* Supports:

  * Gym workouts
  * Home workouts
* Workout recommendations based on:

  * Age
  * Experience
  * Goal
  * Workout duration
  * Workout days
* Beginner, Intermediate and Advanced routines

---

## рџ¤– AI Chatbot

* Powered by **Groq Llama 3.3-70B**
* Answers fitness and nutrition related questions
* Provides workout and health guidance

---

## рџ“„ PDF Knowledge Assistant *(Optional Module)*

* Upload fitness-related PDF documents
* Search only within uploaded PDFs
* Displays answers directly from PDF content
* If information is unavailable, prompts the user to use the AI Chatbot

---

## рџ“Љ Habit Tracker

Track daily workouts including:

* Workout type
* Exercise
* Sets
* Repetitions
* Weight lifted
* Duration
* Calories burned

Displays:

* Current streak
* Total workouts
* Workout completion percentage
* Monthly calorie chart
* Workout history

---

## рџ“€ Progress Dashboard

Visualizes:

* Calories burned
* Workout distribution
* Workout history
* Monthly progress

